20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%2043%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20discussions%20are%20underway%20with%20Kuwait%20on%20a%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20and%20a%20defence%20cooperation%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20media%20briefing%2C%20Arun%20Kumar%20Chatterjee%2C%20Secretary%20(Overseas%20Indian%20Affairs)%20in%20the%20MEA%2C%20said%20a%20few%20bilateral%20documents%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20firmed%20up%20during%20the%20prime%20minister's%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20historic%20visit%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20expected%20to%20open%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20India-Kuwait%20bilateral%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20not%20only%20consolidate%20the%20partnership%20in%20existing%20spheres%20but%20also%20unveil%20new%20avenues%20for%20future%20cooperation%2C%20reinforce%20our%20shared%20values%20and%20build%20a%20more%20stronger%20and%20dynamic%20partnership%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%20said%20the%20visit%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20boost%20the%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GCC%20is%20an%20influential%20grouping%20comprising%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%20and%20Kuwait.%20The%20total%20volume%20of%20India's%20trade%20with%20GCC%20countries%20stood%20at%20USD%20184.46%20billion%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait%20is%20the%20current%20chair%20of%20the%20GCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%20said%20India%20is%20holding%20negotiations%20with%20the%20GCC%20for%20a%20free%20trade%20pact.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20both%20sides%20will%20be%20able%20to%20conclude%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20PM%20Modi's%20planned%20visit%20to%20a%20labour%20camp%20in%20Kuwait%2C%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20said%20the%20government%20of%20India%20attaches%20considerable%20importance%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%20the%20Indian%20workers%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20the%20labour%20camp%20is%20to%20express%20the%20amount%20of%20importance%20the%20government%20of%20India%20attaches%20to%20our%20workers.%20That%20is%20the%20prime%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2045%20Indians%20were%20killed%20in%20devastating%20fire%20in%20a%20building%20housing%20foreign%20workers%20in%20southern%20Kuwait's%20Mangaf%20locality%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20visiting%20Kuwait%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Kuwaiti%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Meshal%20Al-Ahmad%20Al-Jaber%20Al-Sabah.%20Besides%20meeting%20the%20Emir%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20also%20hold%20talks%20with%20the%20Kuwaiti%20Crown%20Prince%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20visit%20would%20help%20develop%20a%20more%20dynamic%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20review%20with%20the%20Kuwaiti%20leadership%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20bilateral%20ties%20including%20in%20areas%20of%20trade%2C%20investment%2C%20energy%2C%20culture%20and%20people-to-people%20contacts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuwaiti%20Crown%20Prince%20will%20also%20to%20host%20a%20banquet%20for%20PM%20Modi%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20Kuwait%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20top%20trading%20partners%20of%20Kuwait.%20The%20Indian%20community%20is%20the%20largest%20expatriate%20community%20in%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gulf%20nation%20is%20among%20India's%20top%20trading%20partners%2C%20with%20bilateral%20trade%20valued%20at%20USD%2010.47%20billion%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait%20is%20India's%20sixth%20largest%20crude%20supplier%2C%20meeting%203%20percent%20of%20the%20country's%20energy%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20exports%20to%20Kuwait%20reached%20USD%202%20billion%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20while%20investments%20by%20the%20Kuwait%20Investment%20Authority%20in%20India%20exceed%20USD%2010%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Kuwait%20have%20enjoyed%20traditionally%20friendly%20relations%2C%20with%20links%20dating%20back%20to%20pre-oil%20Kuwait%20when%20maritime%20trade%20with%20India%20was%20the%20backbone%20of%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait's%20economy%20revolved%20around%20its%20fine%20harbour%20and%20maritime%20activities%20which%20included%20ship%20building%2C%20pearl%20diving%2C%20fishing%20and%20voyages%20to%20India%20on%20wooden%20dhows%20carrying%20dates%2C%20Arabian%20horses%20and%20pearls%20that%20were%20traded%20for%20wood%2C%20cereals%2C%20clothes%20and%20spices%2C%20according%20to%20people%20tracking%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Rupee%20remained%20legal%20tender%20in%20Kuwait%20until%201961%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20enduring%20economic%20and%20cultural%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20were%20formally%20established%20in%201961%2C%20with%20India%20initially%20represented%20by%20a%20trade%20commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmir%20Sheikh%20Sabah%20Al-Ahmed%20Al-Jabar%20Al-Sabah%20visited%20India%20on%20a%20private%20visit%20in%20July%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20high-level%20visit%20from%20either%20side%20was%20that%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Kuwait%20to%20India%20in%202013.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734743220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fuft47gh_narendra-modi-ians_625x300_21_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3