2F116518842.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Dead%2C%2060%20Injured%20In%20German%20Christmas%20Market%20Car%20Attack%2C%20Saudi%20Man%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGerman%20police%20arrested%20a%20Saudi%20man%20after%20a%20deadly%20car%20ramming%20attack%20on%20a%20Christmas%20market%20Friday%20in%20which%20a%20vehicle%20barrelled%20through%20a%20crowd%20of%20revellers%20at%20high%20speed%2C%20leaving%20a%20trail%20of%20bloody%20carnage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%2060%20injured%2C%20said%20rescue%20services%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Magdeburg%20located%20about%20130%20kilometres%20(80%20miles)%20southwest%20of%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unnamed%20suspect%20was%20a%2050-year-old%20medical%20doctor%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20living%20in%20the%20eastern%20state%20of%20Saxony-Anhalt%2C%20said%20regional%20premier%20Reiner%20Haseloff%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20scene%20which%20was%20cordoned%20off%20and%20guarded%20by%20police%20commandos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arrested%20the%20perpetrator%2C%20a%20man%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20a%20doctor%20who%20has%20been%20in%20Germany%20since%202006%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%2C%20calling%20the%20attack%20a%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20what%20we%20currently%20know%20he%20was%20a%20lone%20attacker%20so%20we%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20any%20further%20danger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20vehicle%20drove%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20400%20metres%20across%20the%20Christmas%20market%26quot%3B%20leaving%20behind%20a%20trail%20of%20bloodied%20casualties%20at%20the%20city's%20central%20town%20hall%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbulances%20and%20fire%20engines%20rushed%20to%20the%20chaotic%20site%2C%20which%20was%20doused%20in%20blue%20emergency%20lights%20with%20sirens%20wailing%2C%20with%20badly%20injured%20people%20being%20treated%20as%20they%20lay%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20rushed%20off%20to%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECries%20and%20screams%20could%20be%20heard%20as%20around%20100%20police%2C%20medics%20and%20the%20fire%20service%20officers%20deployed%20to%20the%20litter-strewn%20market%20decorated%20with%20Christmas%20trees%20and%20festive%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pictures%20are%20terrible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20city%20spokesman%20Michael%20Reif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20weekly%20Der%20Spiegel%2C%20citing%20security%20sources%2C%20said%20that%20a%20black%20BMW%20had%20barrelled%20through%20the%20crowd%20at%20high%20speed%20just%20after%207%3A00%20pm%20local%20time%20(1800%20GMT)%20when%20the%20market%20was%20filled%20with%20revellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaseloff%20said%20the%20Saudi%20man%20had%20driven%20a%20rented%20car%20with%20Munich%20licence%20plates%20into%20the%20Christmas%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDie%20Welt%20daily%20reported%20that%20a%20piece%20of%20luggage%20was%20found%20on%20the%20passenger%20seat%20and%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunclear%20whether%20there%20may%20be%20an%20explosive%20device%20in%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20authorities%20have%20not%20yet%20ruled%20out%20this%20scenario%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Magdeburg%20city%20administration%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%2015%20people%20were%20critically%20injured%2C%20with%2037%20people%20suffering%20serious%20injuries%20and%2016%20sustaining%20light%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20had%20quickly%20written%20on%20X%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20reports%20from%20Magdeburg%20raise%20the%20worst%20fears%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20victims%20and%20their%20families.%20We%20stand%20by%20their%20side%20and%20by%20the%20side%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Magdeburg.%20My%20thanks%20go%20to%20the%20dedicated%20rescue%20workers%20in%20these%20anxious%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScholz%20was%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20city%20on%20Saturday%2C%20said%20the%20state%20premier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Series%20of%20attacks%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bloody%20carnage%20recalled%20a%202016%20jihadist%20attack%20in%20which%20a%20Tunisian%20man%20driving%20a%20lorry%20killed%2012%20people%20in%20a%20Christmas%20market%20in%20Berlin%2C%20the%20country's%20worst%20ever%20such%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2013th%20victim%20died%20later%20having%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20in%20the%20assault%2C%20claimed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20State%20(IS)%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Interior%20Minister%20Nancy%20Faeser%20has%20recently%20called%20on%20people%20to%20be%20vigilant%20at%20Christmas%20markets%2C%20although%20she%20said%20that%20authorities%20had%20not%20received%20any%20specific%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDomestic%20security%20service%20the%20Office%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20the%20Constitution%20had%20warned%20it%20considers%20Christmas%20markets%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bideologically%20suitable%20target%20for%20Islamist-motivated%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%20has%20in%20recent%20times%20seen%20a%20series%20of%20suspected%20Islamist-motivated%20knife%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20eight%20wounded%20in%20a%20stabbing%20spree%20at%20a%20street%20festival%20in%20the%20western%20city%20of%20Solingen%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20arrested%20a%20Syrian%20suspect%20over%20the%20attack%20that%20was%20claimed%20by%20IS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20a%20policeman%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20knife%20attack%20in%20Mannheim%2C%20with%20an%20Afghan%20national%20held%20as%20the%20main%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20President%20Frank-Walter%20Steinmeier%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20anticipation%20of%20a%20peaceful%20Christmas%20was%20suddenly%