E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-docs-reveal-contestant-terms-beast-games-preliminary-filming-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeast%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20game%20show%20on%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video%20from%20MrBeast%2C%20debuted%20Thursday%2C%20and%20I%20watched%20along%20with%20my%20elementary-aged%20son.%20As%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20spectacle%20and%20found%20the%20show%20highly%20watchable.%20But%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I%20liked%20the%20message%20about%20money%20it%20was%20imparting%20to%20my%20young%20ward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElementary-school-aged%20kids%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20they're%20allowed%20to%20watch%20YouTube%2C%20all%20know%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-youtube-jimmy-donaldson-net-worth-life-career-challenges-teamtrees-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E%20is.%20He's%20a%20superstar%20to%20Gen%20Alpha.%20His%20candy%20bars%20are%20on%20grocery-store%20shelves%2C%20and%20his%20specter%20hangs%20over%20playgrounds%20and%20lunchrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(My%20colleague%20reports%20that%20his%20teenage%20son%20says%20MrBeast%20isn't%20quite%20as%20cool%20in%20high%20schools%20anymore%2C%20perhaps%20because%20he's%20seen%20as%20being%20for%20little%20kids.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20parents%2C%20I%20want%20to%20teach%20my%20kids%20the%20value%20of%20a%20dollar%3A%20that%20money%20comes%20from%20hard%20work%20and%20that%20saving%20and%20budgeting%20are%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeast%20Games%26quot%3B%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20all%20that.%20Money%20is%20tossed%20around%20as%20this%20strange%20easy-come%2C%20easy-go%20object.%20It%20opens%20with%20MrBeast%20standing%20on%20a%20pyramid%20of%20cash%20(allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-prime-video-beast-games-5-million-prize-youtube-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20full%20%245%20million%20prize%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20stacks%20of%20bills).%20We%20are%20repeatedly%20told%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20cash%20prize%20ever%20in%20a%20game%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show's%20premise%20is%20that%20a%20group%20of%20contestants%20will%20compete%20in%20challenges%20to%20win%20that%20big%20prize%20%E2%80%94%20a%20season-long%20version%20of%20some%20of%20his%20popular%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20season%20there%20will%20be%20physical%20challenges%20(we%20see%20preview%20clips%20of%20people%20pulling%20a%20monster%20truck)%2C%20but%20in%20this%20first%20episode%20the%20games%20are%20almost%20all%20psychological%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20first%20series%20of%20minigames%20aims%20to%20winnow%20the%20contestant%20pool%20to%20500%20people%20from%201%2C000.%20The%20games%20are%20variations%20on%20the%20prisoner's%20dilemma%2C%20pitting%20what's%20good%20for%20an%20individual%20against%20what's%20good%20for%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20game%2C%20MrBeast%20makes%20this%20offer%3A%20Anyone%20who%20quits%20the%20game%20immediately%20can%20share%20a%20pot%20of%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20pot%20gets%20smaller%20as%20more%20people%20choose%20to%20take%20the%20early%20out.%20In%20another%20game%2C%20each%20team%20of%20about%20100%20people%20must%20have%20one%20person%20sacrifice%20themselves%20and%20leave%20the%20game%20with%20no%20prize%20money%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20or%20else%20the%20whole%20team%20is%20eliminated.%20People%20are%20sobbing%2C%20yelling%20at%20each%20other%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a1a7723-c24d-4d8d-bd8a-631185a29ac7%5C%22%3EI%20worry%20about%20the%20message%20'Beast%20Games'%20sends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20fascinating%20challenge%20to%20watch%20as%20an%20adult.%20But%20I'm%20not%20sure%20a%20kid%20can%20really%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wrenching%20pain%20of%20people%