zzle%20boards%20with%20hidden%20treats%2C%20balls%20that%20dispense%20food%20as%20a%20dog%20moves%20them%20around%2C%20mats%20that%20hold%20hidden%20pieces%20of%20kibble%20or%20treats%2C%20and%20hide-and-seek%20plush%20toys.%20Each%20puzzle%20toy%20is%20designed%20to%20engage%20a%20dog's%20sense%20of%20smell%20and%20their%20desire%20to%20hunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20say%20this%20type%20of%20enrichment%20is%20essential%20to%20a%20dog's%20mental%20well-being%20and%20should%20be%20given%20to%20healthy%20pups%20multiple%20times%20a%20day.%20Without%20sufficient%20mental%20stimulation%2C%20behavior%20problems%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20develop.%20%26quot%3BThese%20can%20include%20hyperactivity%2C%20destructive%20behavior%2C%20symptoms%20of%20separation-related%20stress%2C%20excessive%20vocalization%2C%20and%20aggression%20toward%20humans%20or%20animal%20housemates%2C%26quot%3B%20Haug%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20toys%20keep%20dogs%20busy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20dogs%20love%20play%20activities%20like%20tug%2C%20chase%2C%20and%20fetch%2C%20they%20enjoy%20them%20most%20when%20they%20have%20someone%20to%20play%20with.%20Treat%20puzzle%20toys%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20engage%20a%20dog%20without%20input%20from%20a%20person%20or%20another%20dog%2C%20at%20least%20until%20the%20kibble%20or%20treats%20are%20gone.%20Not%20every%20dog%20will%20enjoy%20every%20type%20of%20puzzle%20toy%2C%20but%20the%20majority%20of%20pups%20will%20find%20at%20least%20one%20to%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kinds%20of%20puzzles%20are%20good%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20puzzle%20toys%20are%20not%20the%20only%20way%20to%20create%20mentally%20enriching%20challenges%20for%20your%20dog.%20You%20can%20easily%20make%20your%20own%20dog%20puzzles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20simple%20things%20like%20rolling%20food%20up%20in%20a%20towel%20or%20throwing%20treats%20into%20an%20empty%20cereal%20box%20for%20the%20dog%20to%20rip%20open%20(of%20course%2C%20this%20is%20not%20suitable%20for%20dogs%20that%20may%20eat%20the%20cardboard)%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20says.%20%26quot%3BMy%20absolute%20favourite%20enrichment%20is%20scent%20work.%20It's%20easy%20to%20create%20a%20treasure%20hunt%20with%20the%20dog's%20food%20around%20the%20home%20or%20garden%20for%20them%20to%20sniff%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20dogs%20enjoy%20puzzle%20boards%2C%20Kelly%20admits%20they%20are%20not%20his%20favorite.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20often%20claim%20that%20dogs%20are%20great%20puzzle%20solvers%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20my%20experience%20and%20these%20activities%20usually%20need%20careful%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20He%20prefers%20simpler%20toys%20like%20wobblers%20and%20snuffle%20mats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20puzzle%20games%20good%20for%20puppies%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20A%20dog%20is%20never%20too%20young%20to%20begin%20playing%20with%20puzzle%20toys%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20supervised%20during%20the%20game.%20%26quot%3BEnrichment%20is%20beneficial%20for%20the%20dog's%20whole%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20because%20we%20are%20fulfilling%20behavioral%20needs%20and%20allowing%20the%20dog%20to%20be%20successful%20and%20therefore%20gain%20confidence%20and%20develop%20a%20good%20mindset.%20Good%20mental%20health%20will%20influence%20the%20dog's%20general%20behavioral%20decisions%20and%20general%20feeling%20of%20contentment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-puzzle%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734724909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e04b86d8e3a400192cbb01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-puzzle%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20dog%