imit%20on%20how%20much%20the%20federal%20government%20can%20borrow.%20Doing%20so%20now%20would%20mean%20the%20much-debated%20move%20would%20happen%20on%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20watch%20and%20be%20resolved%20before%20Trump%20takes%20office%2C%20when%20he'll%20want%20to%20implement%20his%20agenda%20without%20a%20fight%20over%20borrowing%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20must%20get%20rid%20of%2C%20or%20extend%20out%20to%2C%20perhaps%2C%202029%2C%20the%20ridiculous%20Debt%20Ceiling%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20Friday%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20this%2C%20we%20should%20never%20make%20a%20deal.%20Remember%2C%20the%20pressure%20is%20on%20whoever%20is%20President.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20comes%20amid%20a%20chaotic%20scramble%20to%20reach%20a%20funding%20deal%20for%20the%20US%20government%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-representatives-continuing-resolution-spending-bill-trump-musk-government-shutdown-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20a%20shutdown%20when%20Friday%20ends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20debt%20ceiling%20was%20one%20of%20the%20sticking%20points%20Trump%20used%20to%20scrap%20a%20bipartisan%20deal%20to%20keep%20the%20government%20funded%20through%20March.%20Now%20he's%20revisiting%20a%20much-used%20political%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20is%20right%20to%20identify%20that%20he%20doesn't%20want%20his%20fingerprints%20on%20increasing%20the%20debt%20ceiling%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20it%20in%20six%20months%20while%20he's%20trying%20to%20pass%20what%20he%20considers%20a%20must-pass%20tax-extension%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20Elizabeth%20Pancotti%2C%20the%20director%20of%20special%20initiatives%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20Roosevelt%20Institute%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226653b78-d5a4-4ff0-9d3e-c3c5279aabc4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20debt-ceiling%20breach%20has%20