%24134.82%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20tended%20to%20be%20most%20enthusiastic%20on%20NVIDIA%20when%20the%20near-term%20data%20points%20appear%20mixed%2C%20but%20underlying%20dynamics%20are%20very%20strong.%20We%20think%20we%20are%20approaching%20that%20point%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20transitional%20pressures%20%E2%80%94%20but%20by%202h25%20the%20only%20topic%20will%20be%20the%20strength%20of%20blackwell%2C%20in%20our%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20already%20feeling%20bullish%20about%20the%20Blackwell%20chips%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20launch%20in%20early%202025.%20Nvidia%20shares%20rallied%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-price-jensen-huang-blackwell-gpu-demand-ai-tech-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20chip%20was%20%26quot%3Binsane%2C%26quot%3B%20boosting%20Wall%20Street's%20expectations%20for%20continued%20earnings%20growth.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chip%20will%20likely%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bdriving%20force%20behind%20revenue%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20next%20year%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20upside%20for%20the%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20its%20new%20chip%20could%20also%20dispel%20a%20handful%20of%20near-%20to%20medium-term%20anxieties%20investors%20have%20about%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20concerns%20here%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20overstated%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20anxiety-inducing%20short%20term%20but%20we%20believe%20irrelevant%20longer%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20highlighting%20four%20issues%20investors%20have%20been%20worried%20about%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b02ed94d-6c23-4070-8062-f75441b322f2%5C%22%3E1.%20Slowing%20production%20for%20Hopper%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20concerned%20about%20slowing%20builds%20for%20Hopper%2C%20Nvidia's%20current%20generation%20of%20AI%20chips.%20On%20its%20latest%20earnings%20call%2C%20the%20company%20forecast%20just%2069.5%25%20revenue%20growth%20for%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20its%20slowest%20revenue%20forecast%20in%20seven%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20slowdown%20in%20Hopper%20builds%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20we%20are%20a%20few%20quarters%20until%20Hopper%20end%20of%20life.%20We%20would%20not%20correlate%20Hopper%20builds%20with%20Hopper%20revenue%2C%20which%20will%20persist%20for%203%20more%20quarters%20or%20so%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20backlog%20of%20builds%20already%20coming%20through%2C%20so%20it's%20time%20to%20slow%20starts%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22983ebca5-481f-4e0c-8fca-de7837d54982%5C%22%3E2.%20Blackwell%20variants%20not%20shipping%20at%20the%20same%20time%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20may%20also%20be%20concerned%20that%20not%20all%20of%20its%20Blackwell%20products%20will%20ship%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Nvidia%20said%20would%20release%20seven%20variants%20of%20its%20Blackwell%20GPU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20hearing%20anxiety%20about%20some%20of%20the%20types%20that%20aren't%20ready%2C%20and%20we%20aren't%20discounting%20that%20there%20may%20be%20some%20timing%20challenges%20with%20some%20of%20the%20product%20types%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20fair%2C%20but%20all%20of%20the%20Blackwells%20should%20get%20sold%2C%20even%20if%20this%20drives%20allocation%20from%20one%20customer%20to%20another%2C%20and%20we%20think%20that%20this%20persists%20all%20year.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20concern%20that%20should%20linger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20Blackwell's%20rollout%20should%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20disappear%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20second%20half%20of%20next%20year%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226cbb999d-d8bc-42ee-901d-58dc9714b7e3%5C%22%3E3.%20Competitors%20eating%20into%20Nvidia's%20value%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20noted%20that%20Nvidia%20has%20seen%20some%20of%20its%20value%20being%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%26quot%3B%20transferred%20into%20other%20chipmakers%20in%20recent%20months.%20The%20bank%20pointed%20to%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroadcom-nvidia-custom-ai-chips-asics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBroadcom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmrvl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarvel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20firms%20that%20produce%20ASICs%2C%20which%20are%20custom%20AI%20chips%20that%20serve%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Nvidia's%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%202025%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20biggest%20users%20of%20ASICs%20will%20actually%20see%20purchasing%20shift%20back%20towards%20GPUs%2C%20based%20on%20conversations%20with%20those%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20our%20forecasts%20for%20both%20AVGO%2FMRVL%20ASIC%20revenue%20are%20largely%20conservative%2C%20as%20are%20our%20forecasts%20for%20GPU%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20GPU%20will%20meaningfully%20outperform%20ASIC%20this%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a34dc59-e18f-4c80-a0c4-b6da9b08095a%5C%22%3E4.%20Less%20demand%20for%20chips%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20AI%20chip%20customers%20are%20seeing%20benefits%20to%20scaling%20GPU%20cluster%20sizes%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20more%20advanced%20computing.%20But%20some%20financial%20backers%20in%20the%20space%20are%20raising%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20returns%20of%20doing%20so%20are%20worth%20it%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3