eportedly%20distanced%20himself%2C%20leaving%20her%20largely%20alone%20in%20her%20final%20years.%20Her%20earlier%20romance%20with%20Dilip%20Kumar%2C%20though%20never%20culminating%20in%20marriage%2C%20remained%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20her%20life%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-kishore-kumar-left-madhubala-alone-during-her-final-days%2Farticleshow%2F116508923.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22France%2C%20India%20Team%20Up%20For%20'World's%20Largest%20Museum'%20Near%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCulture%20in%20many%20ways%20is%20the%20essence%20of%20soft%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20as%20India%20and%20France%20signed%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Ba%20project%20of%20great%20national%20importance%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20museum%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%2C%20which%20will%20be%20located%20on%20Raisina%20Hill%20-%20just%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan.%20The%20museum%2C%20named%20'Yuga%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum'%20will%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20India%20-%20a%20timeline%20spanning%20more%20than%205%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20located%20on%20Raisina%20Hill%20-%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20Central%20government.%20The%20museum%20will%20be%20housed%20in%20the%20North%20Block%20and%20South%20Block%20buildings%2C%20which%20are%20currently%20the%20address%20of%20the%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20home%20ministry%2C%20defence%20ministry%2C%20finance%20ministry%2C%20and%20several%20other%20ministerial%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20-%20a%20project%20of%20national%20heritage%2C%20prestige%2C%20and%20importance%20-%20will%20cover%20an%20area%20of%201.17%20lakh%20square%20metres%20with%20950%20rooms%20spread%20over%20a%20basement%20and%20three%20storeys.%20In%20his%20speech%20after%20India%20and%20France%20signed%20the%20agreement%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20being%20seen%20today%20is%20a%20very%20important%20expression%20of%20international%20cooperation%2C%20one%20that%20is%20built%20on%20exchanges%20of%20best%20practices%2C%20on%20sharing%20of%20experiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20gathered%20here%20today%20for%20a%20project%20of%20great%20national%20importance...When%20the%20South%20Block%20and%20North%20Block%20become%20the%20kind%20of%20museum%20that%20is%20envisaged%2C%20I%20think%20we%20will%20veritably%20be%20seeing%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20remaking%20of%20Bharat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raisina%20Hill%2C%20which%20houses%20the%20two%20identical%20blocks%20facing%20each%20other%20and%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20next%20so%20them%20were%20designed%20by%20Sir%20Edwin%20Lutyens%20and%20Sir%20Herbert%20Baker%20between%201911-1931.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%2C%20which%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20mega%20project%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20history%20with%20respect%20to%20its%20renowned%20museum%20-%20The%20Louvre%20-%20and%20hence%20has%20global%20expertise%20in%20adaptive%20reuse%20of%20historic%20buildings%20of%20archeological%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Louvre%20(and%20its%20old%20wings)%20too%20were%20a%20part%20of%20a%20grand%20palatial%20building%20in%20France's%20capital%20Paris%20and%20the%20French%20finance%20ministry%20used%20to%20be%20housed%20in%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20palatial%20structure%20which%20we%20now%20see%20as%20the%20world-famous%20museum%20and%20landmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mapping%20work%20and%20blueprints%20have%20nearly%20been%20completed%20in%20the%20North%20Block%20and%20it%20is%20currently%20being%20carried%20out%20throughout%20the%20South%20Block%2C%20Culture%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20an%20illustration%20video%20shared%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20his%20YouTube%20page%20highlighting%20the%20salient%20features%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20museum%20to-be%20-%20the%20Yuga%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3QywK7fE-Ik%3Fsi%3DBSzuEXLig8S9HH9x%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20government%20release%2C%20the%20Yuga%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum%20aims%20to%20redefine%20the%20museum%20experience%2C%20offering%20a%20platform%20that%20celebrates%20India's%20heritage%20while%20embracing%20contemporary%20narratives.%20An%20official%20announcement%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20made%20about%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20project%20and%20subsequently%20its%20grand%20opening.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734719280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fmeafl9hs_raisina-hill-north-block-south-block-getty_625x300_20_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-india-team-up-for-worlds-largest-museum-near-rashtrapati-bhavan-7296805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCulture%20in%20many%20ways%20is%20the%20essence%20of%20soft%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20as%20India%20and%20France%20signed%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Ba%20project%20of%20great%20national%20importance%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20museum%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%2C%20which%20will%20be%20located%20on%20Raisina%20Hill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-india-team-up-for-worlds-largest-museum-near-rashtrapati-bhavan-7296805%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22