%20give%20eligible%20women%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%2C%20sounds%20like%20an%20abuse%20(%3Cem%3E'gaali'%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20announcement%20that%20the%20RJD%20would%20launch%20the%20scheme%20if%20it%20returns%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20next%20year%2C%20Bihar%20Science%20And%20Technology%20Minister%20Sumit%20Singh%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20sounds%20less%20like%20a%20scheme%20and%20more%20like%20an%20abuse.%20'Maai%20Behen%20Maan%20Yojana'...%20what%20kind%20of%20a%20scheme%20is%20this%3F%20Who%20gives%20them%20these%20kinds%20of%20ideas%3F%20And%20they%20remember%20all%20this%20only%20ahead%20of%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20RJD)%20were%20in%20power%20till%20last%20year%20and%20he%20(Mr%20Yadav)%20was%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20He%20could%20have%20implemented%20such%20a%20scheme%20then%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Independent%20MLA%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RJD%20responded%20strongly%20to%20the%20remarks%20saying%20they%20reflect%20the%20minister's%20mindset%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP-JDU%20coalition's%20hatred%20of%20Bihar's%20mothers%20and%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20think%20the%20'Maai%20Behen%20Samman%20Yojana'%20sounds%20like%20an%20abuse...%20hate%20not%20only%20the%20mothers%2C%20sisters%20and%20Bahujan%20population%20of%20Bihar%20but%20also%20the%20soil%2C%20language%2C%20identity%20and%20dialect%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20scheme%20in%20Darbhanga%20last%20week%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20said%20eligible%20women%20would%20get%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20help%20realise%20the%20dream%20of%20%26quot%3Bprosperous%20women%2C%20happy%20family%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20foundation%20of%20Bihar's%20Navnirman%20(rebuilding)%20is%20incomplete%20without%20the%20prosperity%20of%20women.%20We%20believe%20that%20when%20women%20receive%20cash%20transfers%2C%20they%20invest%20more%20money%20in%20their%20family's%20well-being%2C%20such%20as%20nutritious%20food%20for%20the%20whole%20family%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20children's%20education.%20By%20directly%20targeting%20women%2C%20our%20programme%20acknowledges%20their%20important%20role%20in%20household%20and%20community%20development.%20The%20multiplier%20effect%20of%20these%20cash%20transfers%20is%20significant.%20The%20improved%20economic%20status%20of%20women%20benefits%20the%20entire%20family%20and%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20had%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20would%20be%20implemented%20within%20a%20month%20of%20the%20RJD%20returning%20to%20power%2C%20would%20enable%20women%20to%20start%20businesses%20and%20help%20families%20fight%20rising%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20Ladli%20Behen%20yojana%20announced%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20last%20year%2C%20which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20BJP%20remaining%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%20Similar%20schemes%20are%20also%20seen%20to%20have%20powered%20the%20victories%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalitions%20in%20Maharashtra%20('Ladki%20Bahin')%20and%20Jharkhand%20('Maiyya%20Samman')%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20in%20February%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20financial%20assistance%20scheme%2C%20called%20'Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana'%2C%20under%20which%20eligible%20women%20will%20get%20Rs%201%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734712140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsa92tnro_sumit-singh-bihar-minister_625x300_20_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com