2%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F113683654440040843%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20previous%20term%20too%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%20Europe%20has%20been%20riding%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20US%20-%20and%20we%20have%20allowed%20for%20that%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20at%20the%20time%20also%20threatened%20to%20stop%20all%20excess%20US%20funding%20to%20NATO%20saying%20%26quot%3BEurope%20must%20contribute%20to%20it%20too%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20US%20government%20figures%20which%20shows%20data%20from%202022%2C%20the%20United%20States'%20current%20trade%20deficit%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20stands%20at%20%24202.5%20billion.%20While%20American%20imports%20from%20European%20Union%20countries%20stood%20at%20%24553.3%20billion%20that%20year%2C%20exports%20to%20the%20EU%20were%20billed%20at%20%24350.8%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20wants%20to%20address%20this%20trade%20imbalance%20swiftly.%20Though%20his%20threatening%20approach%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20it%2C%20he%20is%20convinced%20it%20will%20help%20%26quot%3Bmake%20America%20great%20again%26quot%3B.%20Tariffs%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20his%20favourite%20word%20in%20the%20dictionary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'LOSING%20TO%20EVERYONE'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20his%20resort-cum-residence%20Mar-a-Lago%20in%20Florida%20recently%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20had%20said%20%26quot%3BOur%20country%20right%20now%20loses%20to%20everybody%26quot%3B.%20He%20blames%20this%20on%20%26quot%3Bbad%20deals%26quot%3B%20made%20by%20successive%20regimes%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20in%20the%20US.%20He%20believes%20tariffs%20will%20fix%20this.%20%26quot%3BTariffs%20will%20make%20our%20country%20rich%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20his%20words%2